{"tid":2421011,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【7.28 上環暴動案】控方稱示威者手持浮板 陳仲衡: 與其話拎住 不如話個浮板套喺佢前臂 好似古羅馬人決鬥","createTime":"2021-02-24T08:27:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T10:33:50.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f2f46c8c55fa59d788c2cc63482ae4436aef4109","tid":2421011,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:27:07.000Z","msg":"前年 7 月 28 日，上環爆發激烈警民衝突，24 人被控暴動，當中 23 人不認罪，今（24 日）在西九龍裁判法院續審。控方播放警方攝錄的片段，指出片段中有一人手持黃色浮板，法官陳仲衡聞言謂：「與其話佢拎住，不如話個浮板套喺佢前臂，好似古羅馬啲人決鬥咁」。<br />\n<br />\n現為高級督察、時任西九龍總區應變大隊第二梯隊第三小隊指揮官的吳智偉，今日繼續作供。控方播放警方攝錄的片段，顯示警員多次用中、英語廣播，要求在場人士離開；現場人士則大叫「光復香港，時代革命」等口號。控方指，片段中有一人手持黃色浮板，吳同意。法官陳仲衡聞言謂：「與其話佢拎住，不如話個浮板套喺佢前臂，好似古羅馬啲人決鬥咁」；控方同意法官所述。<br />\n<br />\n片中警員疑認錯袁嘉蔚作周庭<br />\n<br />\n控方又指有示威者監察警方部署；吳同意，稱有人運送物資如膠水馬，但現場沒有留意有人搖路牌，今日才於片段中看到。警方片段不斷攝錄在場人士的「大頭照」，包括途人及記者，亦錄到有警員稱「有黃之鋒同周庭」。不過，鏡頭只拍到黃之鋒、袁嘉蔚及一名穿黑衫的年輕女子，周庭並不在場，警員疑將其中一名女子認錯為周庭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/7-28-%E4%B8%8A%E7%92%B0%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E6%A1%88-%E6%8E%A7%E6%96%B9%E7%A8%B1%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%89%8B%E6%8C%81%E6%B5%AE%E6%9D%BF-%E5%AE%98-%E5%A5%97%E5%96%BA%E5%89%8D%E8%87%82%E5%A5%BD%E4%BC%BC%E5%8F%A4%E7%BE%85%E9%A6%AC%E5%95%B2%E4%BA%BA%E6%B1%BA%E9%AC%A5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F7-28-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%2592%25B0%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2596%25B9%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%258C%2581%25E6%25B5%25AE%25E6%259D%25BF-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E5%25A5%2597%25E5%2596%25BA%25E5%2589%258D%25E8%2587%2582%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E4%25BC%25BC%25E5%258F%25A4%25E7%25BE%2585%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%2595%25B2%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E9%25AC%25A5%2F&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8EBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=f5ac42f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F7-28-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%2592%25B0%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2596%25B9%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%258C%2581%25E6%25B5%25AE%25E6%259D%25BF-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E5%25A5%2597%25E5%2596%25BA%25E5%2589%258D%25E8%2587%2582%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E4%25BC%25BC%25E5%258F%25A4%25E7%25BE%2585%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%2595%25B2%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E9%25AC%25A5%2F&h=79528423\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/7-28-%E4%B8%8A%E7%92%B0%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E6%A1%88-%E6%8E%A7%E6%96%B9%E7%A8%B1%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%89%8B%E6%8C%81%E6%B5%AE%E6%9D%BF-%E5%AE%98-%E5%A5%97%E5%96%BA%E5%89%8D%E8%87%82%E5%A5%BD%E4%BC%BC%E5%8F%A4%E7%BE%85%E9%A6%AC%E5%95%B2%E4%BA%BA%E6%B1%BA%E9%AC%A5/</a>"},{"pid":"7e2c2c041b7a82622cddc1609ba351e00c7ed6b3","tid":2421011,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:31:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d0c6e79ce6c769945d6c6bbb0209d24399b66ea","tid":2421011,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7e2c2c041b7a82622cddc1609ba351e00c7ed6b3","tid":2421011,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:31:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=